    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p>\n<p>Slice the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half and set aside  </p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
