    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>naan breads</strong> to a baking tray</p>\n<p>Spread the <strong>onion mixture</strong> over the <strong>naan breads</strong> and top with the <strong>crumbled goats' cheese</strong> and <strong>black olives</strong></p>\n<p>Put the <strong>naan breads</strong> in the oven for 15 min or until the goats' cheese is starting  to crisp and brown – these are your <strong>Goats' Cheese &amp; Red Onion Flatbreads</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
